{"tid":1007262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登力量集合]尋人啟示","createTime":"2019-02-03T15:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T03:13:49.000Z","uid":92201,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"db27ed979186e4dda388ef6cb4248ed4517cfb93","tid":1007262,"uid":92201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:45:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">跪地拜託呢到所有既連登仔女, <br />\n<br />\n如果見到伯母既請立即聯絡<br />\n61222132馬生<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U670MZW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU670MZW.jpg&h=ca8a0a6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/myLxC6K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmyLxC6K.jpg&h=7e21af41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朋友老媽有精神問題, <br />\n走左落街之後就唔見左, 宜家已經一個禮拜..<br />\n佢最大既特徵係<br />\n著花衫同牛仔褲<br />\n1.5米<br />\n肥身材<br />\n<br />\n27號響秀茂坪邨失蹤, 1號果日有人話見到佢29號響麗港城隔離既容鳳書紀念中心出現過<br />\n最怕係佢會搭巴士, 因為佢有兩張八達通, 有名果張係無record..<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝咁多位連登仔團團圓圓啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1425606/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1425606%2F&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToA5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=d907c6b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1425606%2F&h=b7aae1e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1425606/</a><br />\n警方呼籲市民提供一名在秀茂坪失蹤女子的消息。<br />\n<br />\n59歲女子楊賽娣於上周日（27日）下午離開其位於秀茂坪邨的住所後便告失蹤，其家人同日向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n楊賽娣身高約1.5米，體重約63公斤，肥身材，圓面型，黃皮膚及蓄短黑髮。她最後露面時身穿紅色及白色花紋長袖上衣、藍色牛仔褲及黑色布鞋。楊賽娣的鼻上有一粒疣，身上有錢包及證件。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲任何人如有該失蹤女子的消息或曾見過她，請致電3661 0316或電郵至rmpu-ke-2@police.gov.hk與東九龍總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e122b51198e565db776f787094f1dd300867e5b4","tid":1007262,"uid":1198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:52:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3f05038701d3c7e29d1c65d6cf4ed8b13170e40","tid":1007262,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:55:54.000Z","msg":"俾翻老母人啦"},{"pid":"b209700bd028d0f841016705bd3e7adcd7977edb","tid":1007262,"uid":29269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:57:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d74f748c0e7e86a6a9589b388d86da1ab68b5f72","tid":1007262,"uid":92201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c9836761aee163323c11e9af49865b573c4df8","tid":1007262,"uid":16543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:05:15.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d48c653397a425540ce4af88fe516c8f067d9942","tid":1007262,"uid":92201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6edf84fd0d9012afe542fb64261